We retain your data only for as long as necessary to provide the appâ€™s services.
6. Your Rights
As a user, you have the right to:

Access your personal data.
Request corrections or deletion of your data.
Withdraw consent for the processing of your data.
7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Significant changes will be notified to you within the app or via email.

8. Contact Us
